                     <interp inst="t18191201-173-off976" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191201-173-off976" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18191201-173-cd977" type="crimeDate">25th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-173-off976 t18191201-173-cd977"></join>, one bed, value 2 l.; two bolsters, value 10 s.; two pillows, value 5 s.; two sheets, value 7 s.; five blankets, value 30 s.; one looking-glass, value 1 l.; two counterpanes, value 15 s., and one set of fire-irons, value 6 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18191201-173-victim1733" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           Hutchings
                        <interp inst="t18191201-173-victim1733" type="surname" value="Hutchings"></interp>
